2011-10-07T15:06:24Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-07/emanuel-goffer-sentenced-to-36-months-for-insider-trading.html
Emanuel Goffer was sentenced to 36
months for his role in an insider-trading scheme carried out
with his brother, former Galleon Group LLC trader  Zvi Goffer .  To contact the reporter on this story:
